Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the entrance to the\Ngulf, the statue of Buddha...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who brightens the world with the light\Nof virtue, sits in a sad state.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond it lies the port\Nof immorality, Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the overland entrance to the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's always a noose,\Nhanging for some unknown person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Past it lies the\Ncity of pleasure, Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until recently a businessman\Nliving in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I am now a member of a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bastard! I'll kill you!\NYou're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away! Die, you\Nbastard! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. I'm stepping out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Dutch going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows. It's no concern of ours\Nwhat Dutch does in his free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only asked because I was curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nosy types aren't too popular, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?! I don't\Nknow what you paid for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's worth less than\Nnothing. You got burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so. In this city, the\Nsituation doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...improve in the\Ndowntown core either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta realize, international\Nvillains run around here ramming horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all trick one another,\Nfrom top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not given the right to live\Nif you trust everything you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you're lucky if that's\Nthe biggest of your concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's right. I may still be too soft.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, I don't even know{\i0}\N{\i1}the histories of my peers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their pasts remain heavily masked{\i0}\N{\i1}by their sense of independence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't care. That's how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, it's me. How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,International number 10013. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send me 120 thousand dollars.\NTo the name, Flyers Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to you some other time. Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great weather. Don't you agree?\NHow's business for you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Mr. Chin. We're\Npulling through somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great. By the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan to work\Nwith that Fry Face bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, Mr. Chin. I have no\Nidea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about that crazy Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that Ruskie got\Nhere, the market's been down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Ivans took all the prostitutes,\Nhotel rights, and heroin routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a shred of honor. And if they\Nget the sea routes on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're dried out from head to ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it, don't you? What I\Nmean is pull out, and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you some advice, Mr. Chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even villains have sense. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you sold that junk\Nto the New People's Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we were the ones hired to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't even close to a "no problem"\Nsituation, but who pulled out then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let that go, Dutch. Don't bring\Nup the past like some old bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, Balalaika\Nhas more honor than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ship your goods at our rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get any\Nsecond chances, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you won't get any second\Nchances with us, Mr. Chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head to survive. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Dutch. Why don't you drop some\Nmoney onto us from time to time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's inside your bottles.\NI shipped them here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that the torpedo boat bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...works for some Russian\Nfrom the countryside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. But it seems that they'll\Ntake on jobs from pretty much anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is an unhealthy city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, I got it. The new board's arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the pure,\Nunadulterated, real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pure" is a word you don't\Nhear much of in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry and get it on\Nthe boat, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our crew can really be\Nso damn simple minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, sailor! We have a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay. A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to wash his face, but\Nhe's taking an awfully long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just came in, passed\Non from Donnie Yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donnie Yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gives us jobs from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we're receiving\Na package from...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Vietnamese military\Nat Phu Quoc island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since our schedule is open...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, work is to be respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do with\Nall these pathetic jobs, Dutch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder we can't get him out of\Nthese shitty white collar suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that. I like wearing these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with that aloha\Nshirt I got you at the market?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ugly aloha?! Wearing that\Nwould be pure punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Rock?! You\Nsaying I don't have taste?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they fell for the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you want to go ahead\Nor not is up to you now, Luak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've been down\Non your luck lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you messed up on the last hunt\Nand got chased around by a battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? You take care of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you get all the tolls\Nbetween here and Kalimantan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that lots of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, Dutch. You're not\Ngonna get any second chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this... like this... this... and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this. Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're desperately clumsy. Or\Nare you just not trying hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just not cut out for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this. Look. Even\Na monkey can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. But don't be so hard\Non me. I never did this at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. What did you do at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with the materials\Nprocurement department...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I went on business\Ntrips, wrote reports...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...made phone calls, but\NI think lowering my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to my superiors was my real job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come night, I'd accompany my superiors\Nwhen he'd go out for drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even got my ass kicked once\Nwhen he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a disgusting story.\NPutting up with all that crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some masochist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting up with it is part of the job.\NNo one wants to end up on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone survives like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. What did you do\Nbefore coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I do hasn't really\Nchanged from then to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. Then let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a kid, you ran around by the river,\Nswinging around your Sword Cutlass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. I stole, I killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I did everything that's considered bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing fascinating about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, we've got several boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better pray, Dutch, 'cause you'll\Nneed directions on how to get to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There shouldn't be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...any merchants around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pirate's bay. Can\Nyou find out what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're small and fast.\NThey could be police boats...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...looking to arrest pirates...\N{\i1}Dutch! A red alert!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this. They blew right\Nby the yellow and gave us the red lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their speed, 28 knots.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny will explain the\Nsituation to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a second.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three more!\NA total of six boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first three started accelerating from{\i0}\N{\i1}the side of the island we just passed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other three on port side came{\i0}\N{\i1}from behind a different island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Changing course to{\i0}\N{\i1}port side is dangerous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ships on the left will{\i0}\N{\i1}catch up to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But to starboard, the guys{\i0}\N{\i1}on the right will get us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A basic hunting pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those guys are fast, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey Dutch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know who they are?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks all the way up here.\NThese guys aren't marine cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:14:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys stink too much\Nof blood and smoke for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?! We're being\Ntargeted by pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch! What's the\Nbackground on our client?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. That observation hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been conducting checks on\NDonnie Yen's economic situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello! Can you hear{\i0}\N{\i1}me, Lagoon?! It's me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I see. It's Luak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no prey here. Go\Nhome before you get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's prey right here, Beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An old torpedo boat with\Na nice wingspan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our counterpart has six boats. If it is\NLuak, he's brought everything he's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, all these bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chin got you involved in{\i0}\N{\i1}this, didn't he, Luak?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God must pity you for your stupidity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get a pint of lead in you, maybe\Nit'll put an end to your sleep talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's got us on both sides.\NBut these positions, Dutch...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Rock. Get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna surround the enemy, it's\Ncommon sense to position yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...out of each other's\Nline of fire. Amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard. Don't get too confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you straight to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still four vessels. Dutch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...It's your turn. Give{\i0}\N{\i1}them a taste of "Two-Hands".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's show time. Can{\i0}\N{\i1}you make them dance?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. We're taking a break from\Nthe casual talk about your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to concentrate on this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two on the left, and two more\Nto the right, behind us. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And one more...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do that one last, Revy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll start with the\Nshit on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dance the jitterbug!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's jumped onto another boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I can't see with the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't hit\None of our guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill her! Kill her! Finish her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. Which boat is she on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's working on her{\i0}\N{\i1}fifth boat. Wait...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the third's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is! Shoot her! Kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. My... My ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end. It seems\Nlike you're the one destined...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to dance the cha-cha\Nwith some hot lead, Luak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! How dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch isn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dealing with\Nthese demons any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She defeated the whole group\Nall on her own. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While saying that out loud, I\Nwas having different thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what got shattered\Nto make her like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I must be pretty broken\Nmyself for praising this woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for her destructiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! That stingy Luak.\NHe's failed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot. I'd like to see the mother who\Nwould bring up a child to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shoved a burner up my ass,\Nand then conveniently croaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things couldn't be worse! I'd like to\Nkill that Luak myself, all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving out so suddenly?\NThat's such hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we help, Mr. Chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Never mind. You must have\Nmisunderstood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pathetic rumor going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we sort it out over lunch, you'll\Nsee that any fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can understand what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, you piece of horse shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got nothing to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already know everything\Nwe need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pray. That's about the only thing\Nyou can still do while you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We busted our asses for\Nnothing. So damn stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad. Kinda\Nlike being bitten by a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible, moron. Bullets\Naren't free, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Lagoon Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Japonski! It's been a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is Dutch around?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you went on a wild goose chase.\NAnd you got stuck playing with Chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who told you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a bit too loud to\Nconspire about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was blabbing away about it to\Npractically every group in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so even the dead would've\Nknown what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll make sure nothing\Nlike this happens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pain for you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. It wasn't even\Nenough to give me a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Dutch. I realize it's nothing\Ncompared to what you went through...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'll let you hear\Nsomething amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So-called "pleasure and pain".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cooler than J.B.?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll have a job for you{\i0}\N{\i1}soon. I'll call you then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a call about a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She filled me in on some\Ngossip to lift my spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. Rock. Do you guys\Nhave any plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintenance on the electronics,\Nbut nothing that can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the mental anguish\Nincurred due to external interference...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as your employer, it is my duty to\Nprovide entertainment as compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I propose a trip to the Yellow Flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to drink away our pain.\NOf course, it's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stay there till dawn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided, Benny! Get the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, it's not a job. Wear\Nthat aloha shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.50,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, there are fights\Nthat you must still take on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. Prepare the torpedoes\Nfor surface attack!
